{"tid":47530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《大公報》記者涉打鬥被捕扣查 與梁天琦太古站爭執後報警","createTime":"2016-12-20T11:48:01.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-20T11:57:49.000Z","uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b567050bb3d034cf252499f0e4b8ec82bfe4b293","tid":47530,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:48:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161220&amp;guid=56071588&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161220%26guid%3D56071588%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&d=bRak0I%2FDP4tL1KYXgdcoeEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f8a26615\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161220%26guid%3D56071588%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant&h=16ea6040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161220&amp;guid=56071588&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n與本土民主前線梁天琦發生爭執的《大公報》42歲姓盧男記者，被警方今午於柴灣以涉嫌在公眾地方打鬥拘捕，現正被扣查，案件由東區警區重案組第一隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n事發於今年8月，梁與一名《大公報》男記者在港鐵太古站爭執打架，該名男記者報警指被人襲擊。警方於本月16日以涉嫌公眾地方打鬥拘捕梁，梁拒絕保釋，後獲無條件釋放。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zN1iQG3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzN1iQG3.jpg&h=69ff45ed&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3de06c6bfa356bcd1b4cb02ad83cc9d1b552d09","tid":47530,"uid":26671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:55:42.000Z","msg":"抵撚死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4106668beb07e879ff5cc8e6bfd80c486cbc7ca","tid":47530,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T11:57:49.000Z","msg":"哎喲喲，佢個女有個監躉老豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"